OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear and
OL,6,Fsettled this evening but breezy for
OL,7,Fmost. Overnight, low cloud moves in
OL,8,Ffrom the sea to affect most places by
OL,9,Fthe morning. The wind eases compared
OL,10,Fto the day for many places inland,
OL,11,Fremaining breezy along the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FMorning cloud gradually
OL,14,Fbreaking up to give sunny spells by
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. Above average
OL,16,Ftemperatures inland, around normal
OL,17,Falong the coast, but the breeze taking
OL,18,Fthe edge off the heat.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
